name: Prism Safari
description:
This is my first crypto art and since it's maybe the most modern thing I've ever done on the internet I wanted to use my oldest equipment to make it.

Screen recording of a Philco Ford Safari TV (BR, 1976) with a 1994 Discovery Channel VHS called 'Computer - The machine of the century' and the effects are from the Panasonic WJ-AVE7 Video Mixer
